[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0079","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0079.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0426","title":"Linux Kernel /dev/kmem 默认权限缺陷导致 IP 欺骗漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 2.0.36 之前版本中 /dev/kmem 设备的默认权限设置不当（CWE-276），导致任意本地用户可读取内核虚拟内存空间。攻击者通过读取内核中的网络连接数据结构，能够伪造 TCP/IP 数据包的源 IP 地址，实现盲 IP 欺骗攻击。该漏洞影响 Red Hat、SUSE 等主流发行版使用的 2.0.36 之前内核版本，攻击者需具备目标系统本地访问权限。利用难度较低且影响范围广泛，可导致身份伪造和连接劫持。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0426"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:22.267","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.0.36 或更高版本，该版本已修复 /dev/kmem 默认权限问题。如无法升级内核，可手动将 /dev/kmem 权限修改为 600（仅 root 可读写），以阻止非授权用户利用该设备进行 IP 欺骗攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0426","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19458"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0079.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0079.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0070","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0070.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0419","title":"Microsoft Exchange SMTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange SMTP 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，当 SMTP 服务向目标邮件服务器投递邮件时若收到 4xx 临时错误响应，会快速且反复地重试发送，导致大量系统资源（CPU、内存、网络连接）被消耗，最终造成邮件服务不可用。攻击者可构造恶意邮件服务器返回 4xx 错误码以触发该漏洞。影响 Microsoft Exchange Server 各版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。建议升级至最新安全补丁或配置重试策略限制。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0419"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:21.433","remediation":"建议安装 Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 Service Pack 2 或更高版本，该更新限制了 SMTP 服务在收到 4xx 错误码时的重试次数和频率。如无法升级，可通过修改 Exchange IMS 配置，减少连接重试间隔并限制并发出站连接数以缓解 DoS 影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0419"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0070.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0060","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0060.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0413","title":"SGI IRIX X Server 字体路径缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统 X Window System 服务器在处理字体路径时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过构造恶意的字体路径参数触发该漏洞，覆盖内存中的关键数据，从而获取系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 系统，攻击者需要拥有本地访问权限才能利用。CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0413"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:20.670","remediation":"安装 SGI 安全公告 19990301-01-PX 提供的对应补丁，或升级到包含该修复的 IRIX 版本。鉴于 SGI 已停止运营且 IRIX 已终止支持多年，建议将仍在运行的 IRIX 系统迁移至受支持的操作系统；若无法迁移，应严格限制本地登录权限、最小化可访问 X 服务器的用户范围，并禁用不必要的 X 字体服务以降低利用面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0060.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0018","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0261","title":"NetManage Chameleon SMTPd 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NetManage Chameleon SMTPd 服务存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞，源于对 HELO 和 HELP 等 SMTP 命令输入长度缺乏有效边界检查。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标 SMTP 端口发送超长命令（如 HELO 后跟超过 471 字符的主机名），触发缓冲区溢出导致服务崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上的 Chameleon 4.5 及 UnixLink 97 版本，CVSS v2 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0261"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.477","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Netmanage Chameleon 4.5 及 Unixlink 97 的 SMTPd 服务（Windows NT 平台），由于产品早已停止维护且厂商未发布补丁，建议升级迁移至受支持的 SMTP 服务器（如 Exchange Server、Postfix 等）。若暂时无法迁移，应在防火墙限制对 TCP 25 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接；同时监控 SMTP 服务的异常崩溃日志以及时发现攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.insecure.org/sploits/netmanage.chameleon.overflows.html","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0261","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0261.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9v5m-hg7x-6gfx/GHSA-9v5m-hg7x-6gfx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0261.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x3000/2387/info.html","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0013","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0013.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0223","title":"Sun Solaris syslogd 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统 syslogd 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，当远程主机向目标 Solaris 系统发送 syslog 消息时，若该主机缺少反向 DNS（PTR）记录，syslogd 在处理过程中会发生崩溃，导致系统日志服务中断。攻击者无需认证即可利用此漏洞，持续发送此类消息可使 syslogd 反复崩溃，影响系统日志记录功能。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0223"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.797","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至包含此补丁的版本（如 Solaris 2.6 及以上），或在 /etc/syslog.conf 中禁用反向 DNS 解析功能；同时建议在防火墙层面限制外部主机向 UDP 514 端口发送 syslog 消息，防止未授权来源触发崩溃。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.Sun.COM/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?patchid=103291&collection=fpatches","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1878"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0013.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0012","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0012.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0222","title":"Cisco IOS Web Server 长URL拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 路由器的 Web 服务器组件存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标设备发送超长 URL 即可触发缓冲区溢出，导致 IOS 进程崩溃并迫使路由器重新启动，造成网络服务中断。该漏洞影响启用 HTTP 服务的 Cisco IOS 设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。缓解措施为禁用不必要的 HTTP 服务或通过访问控制列表限制来源 IP。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0222"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.680","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至修复版本（如 11.2(18)、12.0(11) 及以上），或禁用 HTTP 服务：全局配置模式下执行 `no ip http server`。如需保留 HTTP 服务，通过 `ip http access-class` 配合 ACL 限制可信管理源地址，并在接口上应用 `ip access-group` 过滤对 80 端口的非授权访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/60159","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0222","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0222.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0222.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153300_153400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8cfdaab2997679f3e193ea9539f778b75d8c9d41/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0012.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0012.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0012.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0011","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0221","title":"Lucent Ascend 路由器远程管理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lucent Ascend 路由器远程管理服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标路由器的 150 端口（远程管理端口）发送特制数据包，导致路由器服务崩溃或无法响应正常请求。该漏洞影响 Lucent Ascend 系列路由器，无需身份认证即可远程触发，危害等级中危。官方已发布固件更新修复此漏洞，建议用户升级至最新版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0221"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.547","remediation":"在防火墙或访问控制列表（ACL）中限制对 TCP/UDP 150 端口的访问，仅允许 trusted 管理 IP 连接。如无需远程管理功能，建议在路由器配置中禁用远程管理服务（no remote-management）。若设备仍在使用，应升级至供应商支持的最新固件版本，或替换为受支持的现代路由器设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0221","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0221.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0221","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-635x-qr4g-qqp3/GHSA-635x-qr4g-qqp3.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0221.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80896/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0036","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0036.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0381","title":"Super syslog 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Super 3.11.6 及之前版本的 syslog 工具中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 syslog 发送特制的日志消息触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Debian 2.0 等使用 super 3.11.6 的 Linux 发行版，利用前提是攻击者具备本地系统访问权限，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0381"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.503","remediation":"升级 super 包至 3.12 及以上版本，该版本已修复 syslog 函数中的缓冲区溢出问题。临时缓解措施可移除 super 程序的 setuid 权限位：chmod u-s /usr/bin/super，限制非授权用户提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/342","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=Pine.LNX.3.96.990225011801.12757A-100000%40eleet","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19270"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0036.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0156","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0156.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0483","title":"OpenBSD FFS和EXT2FS文件系统nlink值处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 的 FFS 和 EXT2FS 文件系统实现中存在拒绝服务漏洞。由于内核在处理文件 nlink 值（硬链接计数）时未做边界检查，当本地用户创建超过 65535 个硬链接时，nlink 值会溢出并触发内核崩溃，导致系统拒绝服务。攻击者需要本地 shell 权限即可利用，无需特殊权限。该漏洞影响早期版本的 OpenBSD 操作系统。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0483"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:29.640","remediation":"升级 OpenBSD 至 2.5 或更高版本，或应用 2.4 errata 第 001 号（EXT2FS 补丁）和第 004 号（FFS link 补丁）源码补丁后重新编译内核。临时缓解措施可限制不可信用户的本地登录权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6129"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0156.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0052","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0052.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0408","title":"Cobalt Networks Cobalt RaQ 历史命令文件信息泄露漏洞","description":"Cobalt RaQ 微服务器存在敏感信息泄露漏洞。当管理员通过交互式 shell 登录系统后，产生的历史记录文件（如 .bash_history）被设置为世界可读权限，且存储于 Web 服务器可访问目录中。远程攻击者无需身份认证，仅通过 HTTP 请求即可直接读取这些文件，获取系统操作历史、密码等敏感配置信息，造成信息泄露。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0408"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.997","remediation":"在 /etc/profile 或 /etc/bashrc 中设置 umask 027 确保新建文件默认权限为 640；将 .bash_history 等敏感文件的权限修改为 600（仅所有者可读写）；配置 Apache 禁止访问以点开头的隐藏文件（在 httpd.conf 中添加 LocationMatch \"\\.\\.\" 拒绝规则）。如仍在使用 Cobalt RaQ 设备，建议迁移至受支持的 Linux 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/337"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0052.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0035","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0035.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0380","title":"SLMail 远程管理服务 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"SLMail 3.1 及 3.2 版本在启用远程管理服务（RAS）时存在不安全的文件访问漏洞。本地攻击者可将用户的 Finger 文件路径设置为指向任意目标文件，然后执行 finger 命令读取该文件内容，从而访问 NTFS 文件系统中的任意文件。该漏洞源于 SLMail 对 Finger 服务中文件路径处理不当，导致权限验证缺失，造成敏感信息泄露。攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限方可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0380"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.370","remediation":"升级 SLMail 至 4.0 或更新版本，该版本已修复 Finger File 路径遍历漏洞；如无法升级，禁用 Remote Administration Service (RAS) 组件，并限制本地用户对 Finger File 配置的写入权限。作为临时缓解措施，可移除 finger 服务或通过防火墙阻止 finger 端口 (79/TCP) 的外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91996412724720&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91999015212415&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92110501504997&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/497","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/5392"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0035.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1022","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1022.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1247","title":"HP HP-UX DCE/9000 摄像机组件权限提升漏洞","description":"HP-UX 9.x 的 DCE/9000 摄像机组件存在本地权限提升漏洞，攻击者通过向该组件发送特制请求，利用其权限检查不严或输入验证缺失的缺陷，可获取系统 root 权限，从而完全控制目标主机。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 9.x 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。成功利用此漏洞的攻击者可执行任意操作，包括安装恶意程序、查看或篡改数据以及创建新账户。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1247"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-02-24T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.920","remediation":"建议升级至 HP-UX 11i 或更高版本，该版本已修复 Camera 组件本地提权漏洞；如无法升级，立即停止并禁用 DCE/9000 的 Camera 服务进程，并移除相关 SUID 二进制文件以阻断提权路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/advisories/hpalert/006","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2061","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-1247.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1247.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1247","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1247.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1247.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v77g-qpmw-2vpq/GHSA-v77g-qpmw-2vpq.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1247.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87758/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000546.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1022.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0157","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0157.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0484","title":"OpenBSD ping 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 的 ping 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 ICMP 请求包触发该漏洞，导致 ping 程序崩溃或潜在的任意代码执行。该漏洞影响早期版本的 OpenBSD 操作系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。由于该漏洞年代较早，建议升级至已修复版本。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0484"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-23T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:29.763","remediation":"升级至 OpenBSD 2.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复 ping 命令的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，建议限制 ping 命令的 setuid 权限，仅允许信任用户执行。作为临时缓解措施，可通过防火墙限制 ICMP 流量来源以减少攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6130"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0157.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0115","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0115.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0441","title":"Qbik WinGate 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qbik WinGate 3.0、Pro 4.0.1 及 Standard 4.0.1 版本的 Winsock 重定向服务中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的网络数据包触发该漏洞，导致 WinGate 服务崩溃并引发拒绝服务。该漏洞利用了 Winsock Redirector Service 在处理输入数据时未正确验证缓冲区边界的问题，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程实施攻击，影响面涉及上述版本的 WinGate 代理服务器软件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0441"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.220","remediation":"升级 Qbik WinGate 至 4.0.2 及以上版本。如无法升级，在 WinGate 的 Winsock Redirector 服务配置中限制来源 IP 范围，仅允许可信内网地址连接。同时建议在边界防火墙上过滤对 2080/TCP 等 WinGate 默认端口的非授权访问，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD02221999.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/509","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19410"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0115.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0034","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0034.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0379","title":"Microsoft Taskpads 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Taskpads 组件中存在安全设计缺陷，远程攻击者可通过诱导用户访问恶意网页，利用标记为 Safe for Scripting 的特定方法在受害者系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Windows 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害较大。微软已发布相关安全公告修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0379"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-22T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:16.247","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-007 对应补丁（Knowledge Base 文章 218619），该补丁移除存在漏洞的 Taskpads 功能。受影响的版本包括 Windows 98 Resource Kit、Windows 98 Resource Kit Sampler 及 BackOffice Resource Kit 第二版。如无法立即安装补丁，可在 Internet Explorer 中将安全区域设置为「高」并禁用 ActiveX 脚本执行，或避免在安装了受影响 Resource Kit 的机器上进行网页浏览作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1019","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/498","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-007"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0034.toml"}]